-- Casino Removes Diniz From Its Board, Estado Reports
-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 2012-05-12T14:03:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/casino-removes-diniz-from-its-board-estado-reports-correct-.html
(Corrects to say Diniz was excluded from Casino’s board,
not Pao de Acucar’s.)  Casino Guichard-Perrachon SA (CO) 
shareholders yesterday approved the removal of Abilio Diniz from
its management board, O Estado de Sao Paulo newspaper reported,
citing a video transmission on Casino’s website.  Diniz remains chairman of  Cia Brasileira de Distribuicao
Grupo Pao de Acucar (PCAR4) ’s, Brazil’s largest retailer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabiola Moura in Sao Paulo at 
